Subject: perf trace: Add missing thread__put() in thread__e_machine()
Git-commit: 7900938850645ed41770bddba524416f8c84dc2d
Patch-mainline: v6.16-rc1
References: perf-sle16.1-v6.19-userspace-update

Add missing thread__put() of the found parent thread in
thread__e_machine().

